This is a configuration outline. Use it to store searches that you want to show in the sidebar for all TaskPaper documents.

Searches:
	Needs review @search(project Inbox//* union @clarify)
	Today @search(@today union @due <[d] tomorrow)
	Tomorrow @search(@tomorrow union @due =[d] tomorrow)
	Next 7 days @search(@today union @tomorrow union @due <=[d] today + 7d)
	Done today @search(@done = [d] today)
